@startuml
title UC11 — Paid User changes ElevenLabs voice/model — Sequence
actor "Paid User" as Actor
participant "VoiceSettingsPage" as UI
participant "API Gateway" as API
participant "VoicePreferenceService" as VoicePreferenceService
database "MySQL" as DB
participant "ElevenLabs API" as ElevenLabs_API
Actor -> UI : save voice preference
UI -> API : HTTPS request
API -> VoicePreferenceService : route and authorize
VoicePreferenceService -> DB : read/write UserVoicePreference
DB -->> VoicePreferenceService : data result
VoicePreferenceService -> ElevenLabs_API : integration request
ElevenLabs_API -->> VoicePreferenceService : integration response
VoicePreferenceService -->> API : response
API -->> UI : JSON result
UI -->> Actor : voice preference is saved
@enduml
